com.ai.reference

Interface Token<T extends java.lang.Enum<T> & HasPattern>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConcreteToken

    public interface Token<T extends java.lang.Enum<T> & HasPattern>
    Generic token type generated by an instance of a LexicalAnalyzer. This interface defines the minimal behavior for a token generated during the lexical analysis phase of parsing. Specifically, token is a thing that: Has a type -- describing what category a given token comes from (e.g., STRING vs INTEGER vs RESERVED_WORD, etc.) Has content -- the literal string that was matched when generating this token.
    Author:
    Terran Lane
